'''[[A.C. ChievoVerona]]''' played its third consecutive season in [[Serie A]], and nearly equaled 7th place from the [[2002-03 Serie A|2002-03]] [[Serie A]] season.
The club finished 9th in [[2003-04 Serie A|Serie A]] and was eliminated by [[A.C. Perugia|Perugia]] in the round of 16 of [[2003-04 Coppa Italia|Coppa Italia]].
