'''Independent Macedonia''' sport hall ({{lang-mk|Независна Македонија}}) is a multi-functional indoor [[sport]]s [[arena]]. It is located in the municipality of [[Kisela Voda]] in [[Skopje]].

==Uses==
Independent Macedonia is home to [[basketball]] team Torus that plays in the first league.<ref>http://www.basketball.org.mk/?ItemID=849C6C03E74FE04AB6C3875A0C9A2803</ref>
