'''José Ramón Cepero Stadium''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Ciego de Ávila Province|Ciego de Ávila]], [[Cuba]].  It is currently used mostly for [[baseball]] games and is the home stadium of [[Ciego de Ávila Tigres]].  The stadium holds 13,000 people.

